@startuml
title State Diagram (Application Flow)
hide empty description

[*] --> Idle : Application Start

state Idle {
    [*] --> ViewingList
    ViewingList : User browses notes
    ViewingList : Search filter active
}

Idle --> EditingNote : Double Click Note
Idle --> EditingNote : Click "New Note"
EditingNote --> Idle : Save / Cancel

Idle --> ManagingSchemas : Click "Schemas"
ManagingSchemas --> Idle : Close

Idle --> Benchmarking : Open Settings -> Run
Benchmarking --> Idle : Close Settings

state EditingNote {
    InputData : User typing
    Saving : Writing to DataManager
}

state ManagingSchemas {
    ListSchemas : Viewing templates
    EditSchema : Changing fields
}

state Benchmarking {
    Running : Serialization tests
    Plotting : Drawing charts
}
@enduml